Patricia Tallman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Tallman 0 Patricia J. Tallman (born September 4, 1957) is an American actress, stunt performer, and studio executive best known for her starring roles in Night of the Living Dead and Babylon 5. She is the former CEO and executive producer of Studio JMS.
